d and the resurrection, when this </div><div class="t m326 x36 h28 y86b ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mortal puts on immortality, and death is swallowed, </div><div class="t mad7 x29 h28 y813 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">up in victory. 1 Cor. 15:51-54. When we put on </div><div class="t m1584 x29 h28 y150e ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">immortality, we are &quot;clothed upon with our house </div><div class="t m7dc x36 h28 ya7f ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">which is from heaven,&quot; which is eternal. Conse-</div><div class="t ma2 x36 h28 y3b5 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">quently, the &quot;unclothed&quot; state must be the time be-</div><div class="t m13e x74 h28 ybe7 ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">, tween the putting off of &quot;this tabernacle&quot; (compare </div><div class="t m218 x36 h28 y150f ff4 fs14 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2.Peter 1:14) and the putting on of the house from </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
